al\n| length10        = 4:10\n\n| writer10        = {{flatlist|\n* K. Sebert\n* Gottwald\n* [[Nik Kershaw]]\n* Martin\n* McKee\n* Walter\n}}\n| extra10         = {{flatlist|\n* Dr. Luke\n* Cirkut\n}}\n| title11         = All That Matters (The Beautiful Life)\n| length11        = 3:37\n\n| writer11        = {{flatlist|\n* K. Sebert\n* [[Shellback (record producer)|Shellback]]\n* Martin\n* [[Savan Kotecha]]\n* [[Alexander Kronlund]]\n* [[Lukas Hilbert|Lukas Loules]]\n}}\n| extra11         = {{flatlist|\n* Martin\n* Shellback\n}}\n| title12         = Love into the Light\n| length12        = 4:46\n| writer12        = K. Sebert\n| extra12         = [[Greg Kurstin]]\n| total_length    = 44:27\n}}\n{{Track listing\n| collapsed       = yes\n| headline        = Deluxe edition bonus tracks<ref>{{cite web|title=Warrior (Deluxe Version)|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/warrior-deluxe-version/id582338179|accessdate=February 10, 2013}}</ref><ref name=\"JAP\" />\n| extra_column    = Producer(s)\n|title1=|note1=|length1=|writer1=|extra1=|title2=|note2=|length2=|writer2=|extra2=|title3=|note3=|length3=|writer3=|extra3=|title4=|note4=|writer4=|extra4=| title13         = Last Goodbye\n| length13        = 3:50\n\n| writer13        = {{flatlist|\n* K. Sebert\n* Gottwald\n* Levin\n* Malik\n* Omelio\n* Walter\n}}\n| extra13         = {{flatlist|\n* Dr. Luke\n* Blanco\n* Cirkut\n* Wright{{ref|a|[A]}}\n}}\n| title14         = Gold Trans Am\n| length14        = 3:20\n\n| writer14        = {{flatlist|\n* K. Sebert\n* Gottwald\n* Grigg\n* P. Sebert\n* Walter\n}}\n| extra14         = {{flatlist|\n* Dr. Luke\n* Kojak\n* Cirkut\n* Wright{{ref|a|[A]}}\n}}\n| title15         = Out Alive\n| length15        = 3:31\n\n| writer15        = {{flatlist|\n* K. Sebert\n* [[Joshua Coleman]]\n* Mathieu Jomphe\n* P. Sebert\n}}\n| extra15         = {{flatlist|\n* Ammo\n* Billboard\n* Wright{{ref|a|[A]}}\n}}\n| title16         = Past Lives\n| length16        = 3:35\n| writer16        = K. Sebert\n| extra16 